{{Quote|This facility is crude, but it should be adequate to freeze Skywalker for his journey to the Emperor.|Darth Vader|<ref name="Episode 5">{{Film|V}}</ref>}}
A '''class three carbon-freezing chamber''' was a common type of [[Carbon-freezing chamber/Legends|carbon-freezing chamber]]. One such chamber, located in [[Cloud City/Legends|Cloud City]] on [[Bespin/Legends|Bespin]], was used to freeze [[Han Solo/Legends|Han Solo]] as a test by [[Anakin Skywalker/Legends|Darth Vader]], with the intention of using it to capture [[Luke Skywalker/Legends|Luke Skywalker]]. The chamber was later the scene of the [[Duel on Cloud City/Legends|second duel between Vader and Skywalker]].

